channel.title: Them-Us
channel.description: Them-Us.com is a hub of information, tools and entertainment for relationships. Our goal is to start a real dialog about relationships with men and women that goes deeper than surface topics. Them-Us.com is an immersive experience of informative, sometimes funny but always entertaining content that helps you maintain and build healthy relationships. Real relationship talk like you never heard.
channel.itunes:subtitle: Them-Us
channel.itunes:summary: Have you ever had problems with the opposing sex...who hasn't!? If you're one of many out there who have trouble speaking or getting your views across to the other gender then we have a show for you. It's men, it's women, it's unscripted! Listen to guest from both sides lash out and speak their minds holding nothing back. Real relationship talk like you never heard
